{"tid":2494130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6G競賽開打！美國日本將合作投資45億美元 對抗中國","createTime":"2021-04-18T12:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T13:06:07.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"636b2428c58f7ee5357b6419af46ec8f53e169a8","tid":2494130,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/6g%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BD%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93-%E7%BE%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%8745%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8-112345468.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F6g%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2589%2593-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%258745%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8-112345468.html&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=4d93514f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/6g%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BD%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93-%E7%BE%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%8745%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8-112345468.html</a><br />\n6G競賽開打！美日將投資45億美元 對抗中國大陸<br />\n<br />\n編譯林奇賢／綜合外電<br />\n<br />\n2021年4月18日 19:23<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登和日本首相菅義偉在峰會上同意共同投資45億美元，用於開發下一代行動通訊技術「6G」。<br />\n日經新聞報導，根據美日兩國領導人會後公布的文件，兩國會將這筆投資，用於研究、開發、測試和部署安全網路，以及先進資通訊技術，「美國已承諾負擔25億美元，日本則是20億美元」。<br />\n兩方還追求「安全與開放」的5G網路，其中涵蓋開放網路架構（O-RAN），顯示美日領導人有意在中國大陸為首的通訊網絡之外，再打造一套替代方案。"},{"pid":"35ea767bed912acf2ebf34b1daa9b3ff60a6274a","tid":2494130,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6802f02ce75e9da8f641b5b4c285785422f6ba","tid":2494130,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/